data.description: This beautifully renovated 4BR 2.5ba home is light, bright, and incredibly spacious. The living room's clean lines and new wood flooring extend into the kitchen and dining areas. The kitchen features new counters, recessed lighting, and SS appliances. The dining area includes a brick fireplace and provides the convenience needed for easy family meals. The oversized separate family room is spacious and inviting. The Master BR includes a renovated on-suite bath with separate vanities. The home features a new deck overlooking a wooded backyard and sits on a cul-de-sac.
